https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5OjSuf3KuU4WHrHkSZ0P6WhNjTr.jpg Horror - When a group of old friends decide to camp out in the same woods where one of their pals was killed four years earlier, their weekend reunion turns grisly once more as a mysterious creature begins to haunt them -- and hunt them down. At the advice of a geneticist (Chase Masterson), the campers attempt to leave the forest, but it may be too late; the murderous being seems hell-bent on destruction, no matter what the cost. - Kristin Herold, Chase Masterson, Chris Hoffman Creature Unknown
